content.chorus:
Were oso bia kelee Chineke
Were oso bia nye Chineke onyinye
Di mma nwannem
Kelee yan'oga agozi gi
Kelee ya n oga agozi gi
verses:
Chineke enyego gi aku n'uba nk'uwa
Mana o bughi ka I were ya mebisie onwe gi
Onyere gi ya k'iwere ya fee ya n'uwa
Ma binyere ya na ndu ebebe

I Duru Ogaidilya, ya buru na ime chineke
I buru ogbenye, ya buru n'ime Chineke
Maka na a bu Chineke n'enye onyinye nile

I mekata were onyinye Chineke nyere gi
Mejoo mmadu ibe gi
Iga anata ugwo ya
O bughin'elu uwa nke a oburu n'uwa ozo
